This project follows a monolithic Python/FastAPI architecture.

- docs/ARCHITECTURE.md, docs/ROADMAP_AND_PRODUCT.md, and docs/IMPLEMENTATION_AND_REMAINING_DETAIL.txt are authoritative; respect them.
- Do not introduce new services, layers, or technologies unless explicitly requested.
- MVP scope must remain minimal and Meta-compliant. Clearly label suggestions as MVP vs post-MVP.
- Post-MVP only (do not implement now): Media/File service, microservices split, Redis, Celery.
